Wordpress Tips
Wordpress is free software and it is open source. It means you are free and flexible enough to modify it and make it of your own use. Most of the people are in dilemma that wordpress is only used for blogging purpose but the truth, it is widely used for one page template,portfolio, e-commerce site and for other uses as well. You can say it is Jack of all Trades. Wordpress will give you full freedom to edit the source code and make the required changes.
Why wordpress tips are important?
Wordpress tips are all about to enhance user experience of your site. It will describe the importance and usage of plugins which will reduce the complexity of the content management. 
There are lot of plugins and themes are available in wordpress market and most of the people are unaware of the important one.
These plugins and themes will increase the productivity and reduce the burden of managing posts. I will explore and\xa0give detail explanation of the plugins and themes which will be helpful for you to use in your site.
